title: 'Not warm at all'
body: It looks exactly like the photos but useless as a sweater. No warmth at all. It's completely synthetic. I guess that's expected for the price.

title: 'The threads were loose'
body: The media could not be loaded. The thread work is not great, it had open holes on 2 sides, only reason why we couldn't replace it was because we had removed the tag already by the time we noticed the flaw.

title: 'Quality was good'
body: 'Return and replace for the above item did not happen. Waiting for the same. It was supposed to be delivered by 16/12/22'

title: 'Perfect'
body: As I use shirt size XL, so i ordered L size in sweater, it's perfectly fit.

title: 'Nice'

title: 'Worthy for the price point but…'
body: 'The sweater is good overall but it just doesn’t look that premium as you get what you pay for. The cable knit pattern is barely visible and the color is not that vibrant I’d say it lacks contrast. The color is somewhat lighter than mentioned I ordered dark teal but instead of being dark bluish it was more like bluish green. Returned.'
